title: #229 Elbow Bump
description:
Holy hell, it's a show stopper of a Tuesdays as the guys hit up the city's comedy club holiday parties, Mark gets mistaken for an intruder at SiriusXM and Joe deals with a very ill woman at his show in Madison, WI! Check it out!
